#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an3.76"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an3.76:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 3 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 3 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.76:0.2"
msgid "8. Ānandavagga "
msgstr "8. Ānanda "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an3.76:0.3"
msgid "76. Paṭhamabhavasutta "
msgstr "76. Continued Existence (1st) "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an3.76:1.1"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmā ānando yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho āyasmā ānando bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "Then Venerable Ānanda went up to the Buddha, bowed, sat down to one side, and said to him: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.76:1.2"
msgid "“bhavo, bhavoti, bhante, vuccati. "
msgstr "“Sir, they speak of this thing called ‘continued existence’. "

msgctxt "an3.76:1.3"
msgid "Kittāvatā nu kho, bhante, bhavo hotī”ti? "
msgstr "How is continued existence defined?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an3.76:2.1"
msgid "“Kāmadhātuvepakkañca, ānanda, kammaṃ nābhavissa, api nu kho kāmabhavo paññāyethā”ti? "
msgstr "“If, Ānanda, there were no deeds to result in the sensual realm, would continued existence in the sensual realm still come about?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.76:2.2"
msgid "“No hetaṃ, bhante”. "
msgstr "“No, sir.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. VAR: sneho → sineho (bj, s1-3, km, pts1)
msgctxt "an3.76:2.3"
msgid "“Iti kho, ānanda, kammaṃ khettaṃ, viññāṇaṃ bījaṃ, taṇhā sneho. "
msgstr "“So, Ānanda, deeds are the field, consciousness is the seed, and craving is the moisture. "

#. VAR: āyatiṃ → āyati (bj)
#. VAR: () → (evaṃ kho ānanda bhavo hotīti) (mr)
msgctxt "an3.76:2.4"
msgid "Avijjānīvaraṇānaṃ sattānaṃ taṇhāsaṃyojanānaṃ hīnāya dhātuyā viññāṇaṃ patiṭṭhitaṃ evaṃ āyatiṃ punabbhavābhinibbatti hoti. () "
msgstr "The consciousness of sentient beings—hindered by ignorance and fettered by craving—is established in a lower realm. That’s how there is rebirth into a new state of existence in the future. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "an3.76:3.1"
msgid "Rūpadhātuvepakkañca, ānanda, kammaṃ nābhavissa, api nu kho rūpabhavo paññāyethā”ti? "
msgstr "If there were no deeds to result in the realm of luminous form, would continued existence in the realm of luminous form still come about?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.76:3.2"
msgid "“No hetaṃ, bhante”. "
msgstr "“No, sir.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.76:3.3"
msgid "“Iti kho, ānanda, kammaṃ khettaṃ, viññāṇaṃ bījaṃ, taṇhā sneho. "
msgstr "“So, Ānanda, deeds are the field, consciousness is the seed, and craving is the moisture. "

#. VAR: () → (evaṃ kho ānanda bhavo hotīti) (mr)
msgctxt "an3.76:3.4"
msgid "Avijjānīvaraṇānaṃ sattānaṃ taṇhāsaṃyojanānaṃ majjhimāya dhātuyā viññāṇaṃ patiṭṭhitaṃ evaṃ āyatiṃ punabbhavābhinibbatti hoti. () "
msgstr "The consciousness of sentient beings—hindered by ignorance and fettered by craving—is established in a middle realm. That’s how there is rebirth into a new state of existence in the future. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli1.224, sc4
msgctxt "an3.76:4.1"
msgid "Arūpadhātuvepakkañca, ānanda, kammaṃ nābhavissa, api nu kho arūpabhavo paññāyethā”ti? "
msgstr "If there were no deeds to result in the formless realm, would continued existence in the formless realm still come about?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.76:4.2"
msgid "“No hetaṃ, bhante”. "
msgstr "“No, sir.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.76:4.3"
msgid "“Iti kho, ānanda, kammaṃ khettaṃ, viññāṇaṃ bījaṃ, taṇhā sneho. "
msgstr "“So, Ānanda, deeds are the field, consciousness is the seed, and craving is the moisture. "

msgctxt "an3.76:4.4"
msgid "Avijjānīvaraṇānaṃ sattānaṃ taṇhāsaṃyojanānaṃ paṇītāya dhātuyā viññāṇaṃ patiṭṭhitaṃ evaṃ āyatiṃ punabbhavābhinibbatti hoti. "
msgstr "The consciousness of sentient beings—hindered by ignorance and fettered by craving—is established in a higher realm. That’s how there is rebirth into a new state of existence in the future. "

msgctxt "an3.76:4.5"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, ānanda, bhavo hotī”ti. "
msgstr "That’s how continued existence is defined.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an3.76:4.6"
msgid "Chaṭṭhaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
